{"tid":489790,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"古巨基推出全新廣東單曲<無心愛>","createTime":"2017-12-05T04:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T16:32:15.000Z","uid":9030,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c9be3c91b58d4494185ac555fcc60982a49eb14","tid":489790,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"繼12月3號晚晚上推出新碟主打歌&lt;初心&gt;後，昨晚開始於無線播出的「無心法師2」亦發現古巨基獻唱主題曲&lt;無心愛&gt;，這歌是古巨基繼2012年「造王者」主題曲&lt;追夢者&gt; 後，再為無線劇集獻唱主題曲！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eylFNsKSo_w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeylFNsKSo_w&d=NBvsTE65tNIpWvpd1mpTsy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ee961d56\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eylFNsKSo_w</a>"},{"pid":"a9cfa73dd9496d05c6a26e1e3c02eb1e5486365e","tid":489790,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T04:35:30.000Z","msg":"「無心愛」<br />\n主唱: 古巨基<br />\n作曲/編曲: 張家誠<br />\n填詞: 張美賢<br />\n監製: 何哲圖、韋景雲<br />\n<br />\n無懼怕　無念掛　誰造我　這麼的誕生<br />\n如沒心　如沒感　魂在燒　亦是未留印<br />\n乘著風　攜著燈　如像影　步步在護蔭<br />\n偏不可　共你親近<br />\n<br />\n原諒我　原諒我　無辦法　解釋得太深<br />\n憑什麼　拿什麼　來換取　伴聚或甜吻<br />\n由自己　陪自己　流浪於　大漠及城鎮<br />\n只得　這虛空　伴我永生<br />\n<br />\n才學懂　愛要放得開　當思念　超過負載<br />\n沉睡中　最怕夢會醒　消散期待<br />\n望穿生死　望不穿　錯愛與痛哀<br />\n不想一刻快樂　變了傷害<br />\n<br />\n遲或早　痛要放得開　當失落　超重負載<br />\n沿路中　我會在你的　千里之外<br />\n像天跟海　互牽一線　永遠隔開<br />\n陪伴是愛　分開也是愛"},{"pid":"2198d5aa68c865512d4d86e867d61f3f2b3694e0","tid":489790,"uid":16613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:54:32.000Z","msg":"股巨肌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee3df5bcbb053c55e904aa7c1d6aadb6b21978b","tid":489790,"uid":36683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T08:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f5d7f4acba0729d1918158d1878606512d2cf0","tid":489790,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply